<h1 style="font-size: 22px; margin: 0 0 12px;">Stepping in as a fallback</h1>
<p>
  Hi — you're listed as a fallback for
  <strong><%= @tenant.dealership_name %></strong>'s
  <%= @request.metric_key.to_s.tr("_", " ") %>
  for <%= @prompt.scheduled_for.in_time_zone(@tenant.time_zone).strftime("%B %Y") %>.
</p>
<p>
  The primary contact (<%= @source.configured_by_contact&.email || "primary contact" %>) hasn't been able to send the data, so it's overdue. Could you send it instead?
</p>
